    "boxName": "Fuses in the control box",
    "boxDescription": "The fuses of the main devices are in a control box under the dashboard, to the left of the steering column. For access to it, pull the lever with the word \"FUSE\" so that the control box moves to an easily accessible position. Each fuse is stamped with the pictograms which identify the component protected by the fuse. In the centre, in the vertical position in relation to the fuse, there are six spare fuses, one for each amp rating (colour).",
